OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother settled day with
OL,6,Fsunshine for much of Wales. Possibly
OL,7,Fturning cloudier at times near
OL,8,Fnorthern and western coasts,
OL,9,Fpotentially developing into sea fog
OL,10,Flater. Feeling warm with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud across the north and
OL,13,Fwest will drift eastwards at times
OL,14,Fthroughout the night, with a little
OL,15,Frain in places. Turning murky
OL,16,Fparticularly near the coast and over
OL,17,Fhills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
