OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA band of rain will move
OL,6,Feastwards across the country during
OL,7,Fthe morning, with brighter but showery
OL,8,Fweather following behing. Feeling
OL,9,Fcooler than today.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,12,Funsettled on Friday and Saturday with
OL,13,Ffurther rain at times, mainly on
OL,14,FSaturday. Turning more showery again
OL,15,Fon Sunday. Temperatures nearer to
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
